 pet as needed. If 3 were pulled he would take them to zone while I sat in the corner just outside of agro radius. Don't know anything about any more of the mobs though. I will go there anytime if peeps are interested because the last bit I need to really do my epic is there, before the big fights. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/btribalfury31319.showUserPublicProfile?gid=morbier>morbier </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 86<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/15/03 10:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ftribalfury31319frm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=206.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: REQUEST your raid here!! ALSO RAID Formula/ recomendatio</span><hr size=1> &quot;Deep.  Deep.  Deep....&quot;<br>
